Portions derived from MeshCommander
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This product includes software derived from MeshCommander
(https://github.com/Ylianst/MeshCommander), Copyright Ylian Saint-Hilaire,
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The following parts were ported to Go/TypeScript and modified by the
MeshManager authors:

  - The Intel AMT KVM (RFB) client            -> app/src/lib/amtKvm.ts
  - The IDE-R (IDE redirection) ATAPI engine  -> amtd/internal/redirect/ider.go,
                                                 amtd/internal/redirect/ider_scsi.go
  - The Serial-over-LAN / KVM / IDE-R
    redirection handshake and digest auth     -> amtd/internal/redirect/redirect.go,
                                                 sol.go, kvm.go

These files have been changed from the originals; see their headers.

